OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775502669
OL,3,CEA to hold webinar after IT cyber
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FThe Education Authority will hold an
OL,7,Finformation webinar for all Principals
OL,8,Fon Tuesday morning after they
OL,9,Fconfirmed IT system used by pupils in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland were hit by a cyber
OL,11,Fattack last week.
OL,13,FSchools will receive required steps on
OL,14,Fhow to safely and securely re-
OL,15,Festablish C2k access for their pupils
OL,16,Fand staff as soon as possible.
OL,18,FGuidance will be shared with
OL,19,FPrincipals to support verifying access
OL,20,Ffor the users within their school.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
