CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775502669
OL,3,CEA to hold webinar after IT cyber
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FEA implemented a C2k password reset in
OL,7,Fresponse to the incident.
OL,9,FThe EA said it was taking the incident
OL,10,F"very seriously" and apologised for
OL,11,Fthe impact on pupils who may be
OL,12,Fpreparing for exams over the Easter
OL,13,Fbreak.
OL,15,FA password reset has been issued to
OL,16,Fusers of the C2K school system.
OL,18,FThe EA said it could not yet confirm
OL,19,Fwhether personal data had been
OL,20,Fcompromised and it was engaging with
OL,21,Fthe Information Commissioner's Office.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775502669
OL,3,CEA to hold webinar after IT cyber
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"We can confirm that the C2K school
OL,7,Fsystem has been the target of a cyber
OL,8,Fattack," an EA spokesman said.
OL,10,F"As soon as we became aware of the
OL,11,Fincident, the system managers, Capita,
OL,12,Ftook immediate steps to contain the
OL,13,Fissue and begin a full investigation.
OL,15,F"The investigation is at an early
OL,16,Fstage and we are not yet able to
OL,17,Fconfirm whether any personal data has
OL,18,Fbeen affected.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@HO]rD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775502669
OL,3,CEA to hold webinar after IT cyber
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"We are taking this very seriously and
OL,7,Fare engaging with the Information
OL,8,FCommissioner's Office and relevant
OL,9,Fauthorities as part of our response.
OL,11,F"As a critical security measure, a
OL,12,Ffull password reset has been carried
OL,13,Fout across the school network.
OL,15,F"Capita is conducting further security
OL,16,Ftests, and access to the system is
OL,17,Fcurrently unavailable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1775502669
OL,3,CEA to hold webinar after IT cyber
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"We will update users on the
OL,7,Farrangements for regaining access as
OL,8,Fsoon as possible, including
OL,9,Farrangements for password resets.
OL,11,F"These steps are essential in the
OL,12,Fcontext of maintaining the integrity
OL,13,Fand security of the system and the
OL,14,Fsafety of all users.
OL,16,F"We understand and sincerely apologise
OL,17,Ffor the impact on staff and pupils;
OL,18,Fparticularly pupils who may be
OL,19,Fpreparing for exams or completing
OL,20,Fcoursework during the Easter period.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
